          <Text>iMAGES</Text>
          <Text>
            a. Identify the <Latex expression="x" />
            -intercepts.
          </Text>
        </RSLQuestionStatement>
        <RSLCreateAStrategy>
          <Text>
            Determine the points on which the graph crosses the{' '}
            <Latex expression="x" />
            -axis.
          </Text>
        </RSLCreateAStrategy>
        <RSLApplyTheIdea>
          <Text>
            These points occur when <Latex expression="y=0" />.
          </Text>
          <Text>image</Text>
          <Text>
            So, the <Latex expression="x" />
            -intercepts is at <Latex expression="(-6,0)" /> and{' '}
            <Latex expression="(2,0)" />.
          </Text>
        </RSLApplyTheIdea>
      </RSLWorkedQuestion>
    </RSLIdeaWorkedQuestions>

